text: Raymond Dot (20 December 1926 - 30 June 2015) was a French gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics, the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:2015 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:People from Puteaux
